考特尼·洛芙 (Courtney Love) 帮助《最后的晚宴派对》审查了电台《Nothing Matters》的歌词https://www.nme.com/news/music/courtney-love-helped-the-last-dinner-party-censor-nothing-matters-lyrics-for-radio-radar-3576310?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=考特尼爱帮助了最后的晚餐派对审查一切都无关紧要的无线电雷达歌词Will RichardsWed, 24 Jan 2024 13:58:48 +0000 Music NewsNewsNME RadarIndieRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3576310 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-courtney-love-getty-comp.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="考特尼·洛芙" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-courtney-love-getty-comp.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-courtney-love-getty-comp-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-courtney-love-getty-comp-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-courtney-love-getty-comp-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-courtney-love-getty-comp-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-courtney-love-getty-comp-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们对于到底要使用什么来代替[脏话]感到非常痛苦，因为这就是重点”</p><p>考<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/courtney-love-helped-the-last-dinner-party-censor-nothing-matters-lyrics-for-radio-radar-3576310">特尼·洛芙 (Courtney Love) 帮助《最后的晚宴派对》审查电台《Nothing Matters》歌词的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-courtney-love-getty-comp.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="考特尼·洛芙" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-courtney-love-getty-comp.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-courtney-love-getty-comp-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-courtney-love-getty-comp-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-courtney-love-getty-comp-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-courtney-love-getty-comp-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-last-dinner-party-courtney-love-getty-comp-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">最后的晚宴派对</a>透露，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/courtney-love">考特尼·洛夫</a>帮助他们建议如何审查广播中的“Nothing Matters”歌词。</p><p>五重奏首张单曲的原始版本有一个副歌部分，主唱阿比盖尔·莫里斯唱道： <em>“我会操你，就像一切都不重要一样。”</em></p><p>在广播以及最近在英国的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-last-dinner-party-perform-nothing-matters-on-the-graham-norton-show-3574525">《格雷厄姆·诺顿秀》</a></em>和美国<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-last-dinner-party-make-their-us-tv-debut-with-blistering-performance-nothing-matters-nme-radar-3573104">的《史蒂芬·科尔伯特深夜秀》</a></em>的电视表演中，他们将<em>“fuck”</em>一词改为<em>“have”</em> 。</p><p>莫里斯在接受<em><a href="https://www.musicweek.com/media/read/the-last-dinner-party-cover-the-february-edition-of-music-week/089104" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《音乐周刊》</a></em>采访时透露，在音乐节上见到他们时，洛夫如何建议他们改变歌词。</p><p> “我们在《大逃亡》中遇见了她，当时我们很痛苦，不知道到底该用什么来代替（脏话），因为这就是重点，”莫里斯说。</p><p> “演出结束后，她冲上更衣室楼梯说：‘我明白了！’她有一个空包止痛药，上面潦草地写着“打孔”。</p><p> “她有点向我们推销。我们说，“是的，谢谢！”我们欣赏她的热情。” </p><p><iframe title="最后的晚宴 - 无所谓（格雷厄姆·诺顿秀现场直播）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qhC0ZaTD_-0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在同一次采访的其他地方，莫里斯表达了乐队对 Florence + The Machine 的喜爱，他们在 2023 年的一场演出中支持了 Florence + The Machine，而后者最近告诉乐队他们是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-crowned-bbc-sound-of-2024-winners-3565767">​​BBC Radio 1 的 Sound Of 2024 民意调查的获胜者</a>。</p><p> “我们采访过的弗洛伦斯·韦尔奇确实对我们产生了影响，”莫里斯说。 “她的故事与我们几乎相同。她与我们同龄、同一个厂牌签约，在世界构建和讲故事方面对艺术和音乐有着相似的态度。</p><p> “她是如此明智、善良和慷慨。她是我们真正尊敬的人，她是我们身边非常好的人。”</p><p>这支备受瞩目的伦敦乐队和<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-radar/the-nme-100-essential-emerging-artists-for-2023-radar-3372061">NME 100</a>校友将于 2024 年 2 月 2 日通过 Island 发行他们的第一张完整唱片（<a href="https://tldp.lnk.to/preludetoecstasyPR" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预保存</a>）。它将收录最近的单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-shares-smashing-debut-single-nothing-matters-radar-3433299">“Nothing Matters”</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-new-single-sinner-uk-tour-radar-3463558">“Sinner”</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-share-new-single-my-lady-of-mercy-3511842">“My Lady Of Mercy”</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-debut-album-prelude-to-ecstasy-release-new-single-on-your-side-listen-preorder-3528044">“On Your Side”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-last-dinner-partys-empowering-new-single-caesar-on-a-tv-screen-3565601">“Caesar On A TV Screen”</a> 。</p><p>与此同时，《Nothing Matters》上个月在<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/best-songs-of-2023-3-3551141"><em>NME</em>的“2023 年 50 首最佳歌曲”专题</a>中排名第五，而乐队还赢得了享有盛誉的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-brits-announce-2024-rising-star-winner-3555457">全英新星奖</a>。</p><p>他们将于2月2日发行首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-debut-album-prelude-to-ecstasy-release-new-single-on-your-side-listen-preorder-3528044">《Prelude To Ecstasy》</a> 。</p><p>考<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/courtney-love-helped-the-last-dinner-party-censor-nothing-matters-lyrics-for-radio-radar-3576310">特尼·洛芙 (Courtney Love) 帮助《最后的晚宴派对》审查电台《Nothing Matters》歌词的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
