-pikachu-card-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/pokemon-van-gogh-museum-will-no-longer-stock-pikachu-card-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/pokemon-van-gogh-museum-will-no-longer-stock-pikachu-card-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/pokemon-van-gogh-museum-will-no-longer-stock-pikachu-card-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/pokemon-van-gogh-museum-will-no-longer-stock-pikachu-card-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/pokemon-van-gogh-museum-will-no-longer-stock-pikachu-card-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3515703" class="wp-caption-text"> “神奇宝贝 x 梵高”博物馆画廊 图片来源：The Pokémon Company</figcaption></figure><p>由于“安全”问题，这些卡后来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/van-gogh-pikachu-pokemon-card-pulled-from-museum-amid-safety-concerns-3515622">于 10 月份停产</a>。</p><p>一份<a href="https://www.vangoghmuseum.nl/en/about/collaborate/van-gogh-museum-brand-licenses/collaboration-license-partners/van-gogh-museum-x-pokemon#frequently-asked-questions">声明</a>称：“梵高博物馆和<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/the-pokemon-company">神奇宝贝国际公司</a>非常重视游客和工作人员的安全。”</p><p> “最近，一小群人造成了不良情况，导致我们做出艰难的决定，将灰毡帽皮卡丘的促销卡从博物馆中移除。通过这种方式，游客将能够以安全、愉快的方式体验这一特殊的神奇宝贝绘画收藏以及博物馆的其他部分。”</p><p>据<em>Het Parool</em>报道，一名员工涉嫌盗用一盒此类门票，博物馆发言人向该媒体证实，该事件目前正在处理中，并且根据多个消息来源，其他员工正在帮助游客购买门票对于卡片。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-day-before">The Day Before</a></em>开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/fntastic">Fntastic</a>在一份长篇声明中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-day-before-developer-claims-hate-campaign-sank-controversial-game-3576233">声称，一场“仇恨运动”</a>导致了游戏的失败。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/van-gogh-museum-employees-suspended-over-pokemon-incident-3576268">梵高博物馆员工因《精灵宝可梦》“事件”而被停职的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
柏林参议院在文化抵制后的抗议中废除了有争议的艺术资助“反歧视条款” https://www.nme.com/news/music/berlin-senate-scraps-controversial-anti-discrimination-clause-for-arts-funding-amid-protests-after-culture-boycott-3576288?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=柏林参议院碎片有争议的反歧视条款为艺术资助在文化抵制后的抗议中Hollie GeraghtyWed, 24 Jan 2024 13:10:47 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3576288 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joe-chialo-berlin-anti-discrimination-clause-arts.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="乔·基亚洛" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joe-chialo-berlin-anti-discrimination-clause-arts.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joe-chialo-berlin-anti-discrimination-clause-arts-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joe-chialo-berlin-anti-discrimination-clause-arts-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joe-chialo-berlin-anti-discrimination-clause-arts-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joe-chialo-berlin-anti-discrimination-clause-arts-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joe-chialo-berlin-anti-discrimination-clause-arts-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这一决定是在批评该条款会惩罚那些公开反对以色列国、声援巴勒斯坦的人之后作出的。</p><p>在文化抵制首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/berlin-senate-scraps-controversial-anti-discrimination-clause-for-arts-funding-amid-protests-after-cultural-boycott-3576288">之后，柏林参议院在抗议活动中废除了有争议的艺术资助“反歧视条款”</a> 。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joe-chialo-berlin-anti-discrimination-clause-arts.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="乔·基亚洛" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joe-chialo-berlin-anti-discrimination-clause-arts.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joe-chialo-berlin-anti-discrimination-clause-arts-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joe-chialo-berlin-anti-discrimination-clause-arts-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joe-chialo-berlin-anti-discrimination-clause-arts-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joe-chialo-berlin-anti-discrimination-clause-arts-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/joe-chialo-berlin-anti-discrimination-clause-arts-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在艺术和娱乐行业人士抵制之后，柏林参议院废除了一项有争议的艺术资助“反歧视条款”。</p><p>该条款于去年 12 月提出，要求政府艺术资助的接受者放弃“根据国际大屠杀纪念联盟 [IHRA] 对反犹太主义的定义，任何形式的反犹太主义”，并声明他们支持“多元化社会”。</p><p>接下来的几周，近 1500 名艺术家签署了一封来自罢工德国运动的<a href="https://strikegermany.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">公开信</a>，该运动呼吁抵制国家资助的文化活动，声称“使用麦卡锡主义政策”压制了与展览相关的“言论自由”。声援巴勒斯坦并批评以色列国家。</p><p><a href="https://holocaustremembrance.com/resources/working-definition-antisemitism">国际大屠杀纪念联盟（IHRA）</a>对反犹太主义的定义引用了一些例子，包括“将当代以色列的政策与纳粹的政策进行比较”和“否认犹太人民的自决权，例如，声称存在以色列国是一种种族主义行为”。</p><p>罢工德国声称，IHRA 的定义“日益成为官方国家政策，有效地审查了对以色列国的批评和德国文化领域的反犹太复国主义观点，进一步加剧了危险的虚假对等，最终损害了反犹太主义的斗争”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C2a6fRXIxxG/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; ma